BREAKING: DOH reports 1,233 new COVID-19 cases (848 Fresh, 385 Late), 42 new deaths, and 286 new recoveries. 

This brings the totals to 52,914 confirmed cases, 1,360 deaths, and 13,230 recoveries as of today, July 10. #COVID19PH | @shailagarde https://t.co/2bSaqAMW1A
